    "body" : "<p>You may assign <code>'\\u0000'</code> (or 0).\nFor this purpose, use <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Character.html#MIN_VALUE\"><code>Character.MIN_VALUE</code></a>.</p>\n\n<pre><code>Character ch = Character.MIN_VALUE;\n</code></pre>\n"
