    "answer_id" : 24230273,
    "question_id" : 8534178,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>char</code> means exactly one character. You can't assign zero characters to this type.</p>\n\n<p>That means that there is no char value for which <code>String.replace(char, char)</code> would return a string with a diffrent length.</p>\n"
  }, {
