    "body" : "<p>String before = EMPTY_SPACE+TAB+&quot;word&quot;+TAB+EMPTY_SPACE</p>\n<p>Where\nEMPTY_SPACE = &quot; &quot;  (this is String)\nTAB         = '\\t' (this is Character)</p>\n<p>String after = before.replaceAll(&quot; &quot;, &quot;&quot;).replace('\\t', '\\0')\nmeans\nafter = &quot;word&quot;</p>\n"
